<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="correct-vt">correct <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kə'rekt/    美 /kə'rekt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>改正；纠正；校正；矫正：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One learns a language by making mistakes and correcting them.
人们通过不断犯错误并改正错误来学习语言。</p><footer>2012 北京</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new glasses will correct your sight.
这副新眼镜会矫正你的视力。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>correctly /kə'rektli/ adv   </p></div>